snippet.textDisplay:
hum to maail ba karam hain, koi saail hi nahi
raah dikhayein kise, rahbar o manzil hi nahi
tarbiet aam to hai johar qabil hi nahi
jis se taamir ho aadam ki yeh wo gul hi nahi
koi qabil ho to hum shaan bhi keyi dete hain
dhoondne wale ko to dunia bhi neyi dete hain.

I remember reading shikwa and jawab e shikwa in 9th class was my favourite thing to do. Tears in eyes when he said ki Muhammad S.A.W se wafa tu ne to hum tere hain. This sher got stucked and cemented on the inner walls of my heart from childhood. Coke Studio has played a master stroke by selecting shikwa and jawab e shikwa as this is very close to the heart of the Muslims of Pakistan, India and subcontinent. I knew that Coke Studio is going above the previous heights as soon as I got to know that Ali Noor is now the head. He is a gem really. All his songs in previous seasons were master class. From bas kari o yaar to Ghareya. He is a gem. Love coke studio forever. Go touch new heights.
